    <p>Conclusion</p>
    <p>This study proposed a technique to enlarge co</p>
    <p>citation networks by incorporating satellite</p>
    <p>documents in scientific paper searches</p>
    <p>Retrieval methods using the proposed technique</p>
    <p>tended to outperform the baseline method, which</p>
    <p>was based on the initial co-citation network</p>
